{"tid":627761,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【心得】A Way Out 真毒兄弟 中文劇情翻譯","createTime":"2018-04-13T08:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T19:28:02.000Z","uid":150009,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f49a99f50467936064b50031b00677b522a3b87","tid":627761,"uid":150009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/163637_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F163637_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=8736f48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所謂中文劇情翻譯就係人肉翻譯，務求大家唔洗用辣殺漢化、唔洗睇殘體</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n市面上既漢化包大多都翻譯得不論不類 <br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全部都係中文，但夾埋一齊一句都睇唔明</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n所以希望翻譯出更具味道的譯本等大家睇得開心流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時亦能夠細味遊戲中既劇情小細節。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">戴定個頭盔( 所有翻譯都不完全準確) 希望巴絲hi 細力D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無論巴絲中唔中意都好，都可以比下意見小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一集<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YD-O-fV_UtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYD-O-fV_UtY&d=wKwydBehBStME9sSWVBXML%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a7e17ad0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YD-O-fV_UtY</a>"},{"pid":"ccc425b49e0b09c17f1205185e4c91b7f10e6c3b","tid":627761,"uid":150009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:34:13.000Z","msg":"第二集<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rjLqXf-elRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrjLqXf-elRU&d=wKwydB